thread.title: Yami Gautam, the Brand sweetheart

author: CanIndia News Service 1
title: Yami Gautam, the Brand sweetheart
text:
Yami, who just came back from Canada shooting for her up and coming release, has been on a starting spree. The on-screen character has been sought after from brand houses to launch their particular items. 
In the most recent couple of days alone the performing artist went to Delhi and Pune notwithstanding going to occasions in Mumbai.Yami partook in launching a well known cell phone brand in Mumbai a week ago. 
Prior that week, she traveled to Delhi to launch a line of renowned attire brand collection. 
The young woman has likewise been made the new face of a well known Jewelry & Gems line furthermore went by Pune to inaugurate the brands new store. 
One week from now as well, the performing artist will be seen showing up for two occasions to divulge different products. 
The line up of items going from devices to garments collections beyond any doubt infer the significance the youthful performer has with the masses making her the first pick of numerous brands. Related Posts
